# ───────────────── Monorepo-wide ignores ─────────────────
# There is no root package.json — each tree (backend/, frontend/nextjs/) has its
# own .gitignore with tree-specific rules. The patterns here are a defensive net
# that applies at every depth across the whole repo.

# Dependencies
node_modules/

# Build outputs
.next/
dist/
build/
out/

# Real env files. An exact `.env` at any depth is always a secret file — never
# commit it. Per-tree .gitignore files cover `.env.local` / `.env.*`. NOTE:
# frontend/nextjs/.env.production is INTENTIONALLY committed (it holds only the
# non-secret public NEXT_PUBLIC_API_BASE_URL that is inlined into the client
# bundle anyway), so it is deliberately NOT ignored.
.env

# Logs
*.log

# Prisma generate (Windows EPERM) stray temp artifacts
*.tmp

# OS / editor cruft
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.idea/
.vscode/

# Scratch / generated dumps
appendix_*.txt

# Generated demo credentials (contains plaintext passwords — never commit)
DEMO_USERS.md
DEMO_USERS.json

# Legacy scratch note (distinct from the tracked CLAUDE.md project instructions)
Claude.md
